DATASET INTEGRATION

Decision: Merge PhiUSIIL and StealthPhisher only
- LegitPhish excluded (column mismatch without proportional gain)
- Malicious URLs reserved for future work (raw URLs need full extraction)

Merge Process:
1. Kept 10 shared columns + URL + label
2. Added 'source' column to track origin
3. Stacked vertically (concatenated)
4. Applied financial feature engineering to all URLs

Final Dataset:
- 572,119 rows
- 27 features (10 shared + 14 financial + URL + label + source)
- 310,656 phishing samples
- 261,463 legitimate samples
- Well-balanced ratio (54% phishing, 46% legit)
